<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318162>
    dc:description "Figure 4. The holotype of Cyrtodactylus ngopensis sp. nov. (MZMU2553): (a) dorsal view; (b) ventral view; (c) details of dorsal pholidosis; (d) dorsal view of head; (e) lateral view of head; (f) ventral view of head." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318162/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318164>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Live specimens of Cyrtodactylus ngopensis sp. nov.: (a) holotype, MZMU2553; (b) paratype, MZMU2552; (c) paratype, MZMU2554; (d) paratype, MZMU2555; (e) paratype, MZMU2556; (f) uncollected individual." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318164/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7318166>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Habitats of Cyrtodactylus ngopensis sp. nov. from Ngopa, Mizoram, Northeast India: (a) collection site of the holotype at Tuikhur veng, Chawngbawla section, Ngopa; (b) collection site of paratypes at NEC road, Khuangchera section, Ngopa; (c) collection site of paratypes at Taitesena section, Ngopa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7318166/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

